{"tid":968703,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"環球足球獎：C.朗連續3年獲最佳球員","createTime":"2019-01-04T12:33:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T03:36:22.000Z","uid":173952,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6ac4ca9919ea792b8e876e9271a3bd6bc22f0b7c","tid":968703,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T12:33:49.000Z","msg":"2018環球足球獎最佳球員：C.朗拿度<br />\n<br />\n　　香港時間今天淩晨，環球足球頒獎典禮在杜拜舉行，C.朗拿度連續三年獲得最佳球員獎，此外還獲得最佳入球獎；迪甘斯當選最佳教練。<br />\n<br />\n　　2018年，C.朗拿度隨皇馬完成歐聯三連冠。這是C.朗拿度第5次獲得最佳球員獎，分別為2011年、2014年、2016-2018年。法卡奧、列貝利、美斯分別獲得1次最佳球員獎。<br />\n<br />\n　　最佳教練方面，迪甘斯2018年率法國隊獲得世界盃冠軍，他本人首次獲得此次獎項。另外2012-2017年的得主分別是摩連奴、干地、安察洛堤、韋莫斯、山度士、施丹。"},{"pid":"87cc5c2ec27e736354cc82688bcf839065d879fe","tid":968703,"uid":52087,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T13:57:33.000Z","msg":"唔係話咩<br />\n<br />\n講真真係無聽過呢個獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47f9f1a1666fb6d5350d45d028524be174247a1f","tid":968703,"uid":43809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T17:55:50.000Z","msg":"環球時報搞嘅？"},{"pid":"ee24a2c9104898313a1deae9e8c7bd81de0a3bdc","tid":968703,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T03:23:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QdaRRuKRbzQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQdaRRuKRbzQ&d=vHyf5baue3w8D1H4jf3BszCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=ad47b5d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QdaRRuKRbzQ</a>"},{"pid":"b9a7af3022ca7da34db65327c09dd3fee74cfedc","tid":968703,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T03:24:25.000Z","msg":"公平過金球獎啦"},{"pid":"9dba698d473150bfdfe50dce3fb492dee5ba9677","tid":968703,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T03:36:06.000Z","msg":"9650鎊幾抵屌"},{"pid":"c3e482d963b0cccc44a8500f172e013ce54430fc","tid":968703,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":